      passage: `The 1970 founding of the Partido Nacional de La Raza Unida and the 1946 <em>Mendez v. Westminster</em> court decision are important events in US civil rights _____ former establishing a Latino rights advocacy group and the latter legally affirming the rights of Latino students.`,
